{"type": "article", "id": 25704, "title": "球形风扇", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113645kFnwrOJNU2VI39xi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">天气渐渐热起来后就格外需要一个桌面小风扇，这个可用 USB 接口充电的球形风扇也许能作为一个参考。球形的风扇罩只有大概 10 厘米的直径，可以直接用手来调整扇叶的方向，简单而实用。它在技术上的重要特点是可以保持静音。韩国的设计工作室 11+ 推出了红、蓝、灰三种颜色，售价 47 美元，<a href=\"http://elevenpl.us/product/o-fan/\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113643kcHJgDy01dAmb5ei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113643adQqScJgGBH4DKCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.69070905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113644mcyAYVQl2d8xMvnb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113644lizTKpq2Mtdcv1QL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113645Qy75vs10nRfI4acV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}